{"tid":712261,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個提升英文能力","createTime":"2018-06-22T03:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T14:24:26.000Z","uid":184957,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"dde4b290934e4639b7804c12d2722e5935452064","tid":712261,"uid":184957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"想提升下自己英文能力<br />\n<br />\n本身唔抗拒英文 底子正常<br />\n但只限正常 想個能力去到中上 <br />\n主要想for interview <br />\n考官出個題目都即刻答到佢<br />\n其次就係聽得明啲鬼佬口音<br />\n又唔會詞窮 表達到所想<br />\n<br />\n知方法有好多 都不外乎<br />\n睇多啲英文書聽英文歌睇美劇<br />\n睇bbc/scmp/ 新聞 <br />\n搵個外國人同你練個啲 <br />\n<br />\n但想聽下有無人<br />\n由英文底子麻麻/正常 <br />\n去到依家英文對答如流 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間個過程用左幾耐 係點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知好知定題目名為咩好<br />\n方法有好多 但想知入手方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fbaead85a107c7222d5d6520224f86ec4b49e6","tid":712261,"uid":87433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T03:54:13.000Z","msg":"溝鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fa3feb685296b99b390bc39bd7aa5a97eaa7ab","tid":712261,"uid":2442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"睇美劇唔好睇字幕"},{"pid":"b05a0b5d5a12eb5c94ae4d314441431c88cde2f6","tid":712261,"uid":16080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"83fa3feb685296b99b390bc39bd7aa5a97eaa7ab","tid":712261,"uid":2442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:00:25.000Z","msg":"睇美劇唔好睇字幕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"搵一套有興趣嘅美劇（最好現代setting)，搵一集你鐘意嘅做材料，唔開字幕<br />\n每次聽唔明/唔肯定都pause一pause，用netflix嘅話就rewind 10秒再聽<br />\n聽多幾次都唔明就開字幕，諗返自己點解聽唔明，最好自己讀幾次l<br />\n一開始可能會辛苦，但試一兩集可能已經會有小成，因為好多時聽唔明唔係因為個字難，反而係最簡單嘅字連埋一齊讀你聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 為學英文睇劇就唔好預可以好好地enjoy個劇情，當然剩咁睇睇多啲都會有幫助，但個人認為要學好任何嘢難免會有啲無可避免嘅痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350ba7904c3905ae6fc7e8c68caae6910cfe396c","tid":712261,"uid":190418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"打online game 例如rb6 war thunder ,等有in game chat 的game .和隊友溝通時儘量用簡潔的英文，練下練下就得架啦。<br />\n或者youtube game 片，通常語速夠快，貼近時事，有口音，不錯的練習對象"},{"pid":"00bb647bac5d21bcef10a65066a7765fb001fc4c","tid":712261,"uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"練口語可以search<br />\nAmerican Accent Training<br />\n練基本Intonation 一個月就得"},{"pid":"27c3eff74bd8276f4d560a19f0208920621250d7","tid":712261,"uid":184957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00bb647bac5d21bcef10a65066a7765fb001fc4c","tid":712261,"uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"練口語可以search<br />\nAmerican Accent Training<br />\n練基本Intonation 一個月就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"好似幾好咁喎 第一次聽AAT<br />\n書局應該有依本書買呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://dl.ueb.edu.vn/bitstream/1247/2927/1/American%20Accent%20Training.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdl.ueb.edu.vn%2Fbitstream%2F1247%2F2927%2F1%2FAmerican%2520Accent%2520Training.pdf&d=RpIL%2BEEzppGsfSiXGw8IIL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=9c59876c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://dl.ueb.edu.vn/bitstream/1247/2927/1/American%20Accent%20Training.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"fc9662bbdd4820eebba55946a70416254ffdd441","tid":712261,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:51:51.000Z","msg":"Interview 英文真係好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15325a8dd10771d784cffbecc4c963c2e435a215","tid":712261,"uid":180841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":